Homex Reduced to ‘Neutral’ at Bank of America on Valuation

-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 
2011-02-17T13:35:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/homex-reduced-to-neutral-at-bank-of-america-on-valuation.html
Desarrolladora Homex SAB,  Mexico ’s
largest homebuilder, was cut to “neutral” from “buy” at Bank
of America Corp., which cited the stock’s valuation. Bank of
America also reduced its price estimate on Homex shares to 72
pesos from 76 pesos, according to a report dated today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Manuel Rodriguez in Mexico City at 
